{"tid":620430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰開打】網民寸「愚者建牆」係指桑罵槐 《人民日報》急撤文","createTime":"2018-04-07T14:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T02:16:06.000Z","uid":54373,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4043ac4d529c54e1e1d1ca4d27775c06ca2978","tid":620430,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"(互聯網)<br />\n中美貿易戰一觸即發，官媒《人民日報》昨晚在微博發文，引用「智者建橋，愚者建牆」批評美國掀起貿易戰。大陸同一時間，自建網絡「長城」，限制民眾網絡自由，網民指「愚者建牆」是自打耳光，還有人稱這是「妄議國策」。《人民日報》事後尷尬刪文。<br />\n<br />\n大陸實施嚴格的網路管制，禁止民眾瀏覽海外敏感資訊，被稱為「防火長城」，英文簡稱GFW（Great Firewall）。大陸網民必須使用私人虛擬軟體（VPN）才有機會「翻牆」看到遭限制的外國網站內容。<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》官方微博昨晚11時44分發文稱，美國挑起對華貿易戰，商務部已擬定反制措施，外交部強勢回應：「來而不往非禮也，我們會奉陪到底。」發文還稱，「智者建橋，愚者建牆。世界前兩大經濟體一損俱損，魯莽任性絕不會贏。經濟全球化的大勢不可逆，世界經濟絕不能從大海退回到湖泊。維護中國合法權益，我們一不會怕，二不會躲。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n惟大陸網民紛紛留言對「愚者建牆」作文章。有人說這是「諷刺GFW」、「指桑罵槐」、「妄議國策」，並稱要向當局舉報；有人說這是「自己罵自己」。還有許多人叫好，「看了一眼這『智者建橋，愚者建牆』，然後又看了一眼我的VPN，嗯，說得真好，給小編點個讚!」；「建牆是傻逼，人民日報罵得好!」。許多網民表示不敢相信這句話會從《人民日報》出來。<br />\n<br />\n大陸網民表示，人民日報應該是看到網民如此反應後，尷尬把文給刪了，但大家早已截圖瘋狂轉發，引為笑談。"},{"pid":"0f7628738b465b78a790d03c0c2f153e1c2b8631","tid":620430,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T14:44:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53054c2c115300b8629d6fcbcc78cec50f999880","tid":620430,"uid":135408,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T14:49:46.000Z","msg":"以為講侵侵整牆"},{"pid":"cf6933de868c829258c19f71ffd34058d7fd48fa","tid":620430,"uid":82382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T14:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好"},{"pid":"ec70a4254895b3b70de4d49dfbcfa5de3ceb79e6","tid":620430,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T14:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6abbfceafecee7a0479ea4cd2f4bfd0d4302703","tid":620430,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4700ba319038c293b95b7aa3389947539a33dba","tid":620430,"uid":91721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:40:25.000Z","msg":"人民日報黃皮白心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e699cc0f43dce68ec501875eeb161992005ce0","tid":620430,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:44:51.000Z","msg":"根本就柒既"},{"pid":"e0be4f09b618a15197d848a5275d47779bc7ebca","tid":620430,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c813ede6a170807533e3e34d356cfa9661c99b","tid":620430,"uid":40628,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/173931_4efdd2f969559e8b1c92e99f32ded48e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F173931_4efdd2f969559e8b1c92e99f32ded48e.jpg&h=98342452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時啲蠢人都可以起橋架"},{"pid":"3e78378de69880c5330ac1e967b5a4f7b04fc504","tid":620430,"uid":100276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:43:08.000Z","msg":"共產黨唯一德政，就係網上鎖住支那蟲"},{"pid":"ac2e3bb3797d5a8ce4b3471e9bd693de14ba98f3","tid":620430,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16c813ede6a170807533e3e34d356cfa9661c99b","tid":620430,"uid":40628,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/173931_4efdd